
=this readme file is best read using org-mode in emacs=

* Configuration:
- this directory of my conf-scripts contains my emacs configuration. I stole most of if from my good friend, Matthew Ball [fn:1].
- this config is designed for:
  + GNU Emacs
    - Version: 24.1.50.2

** Linking Files
- git clone, and do this symlinking. ### TODO: write a script to do this
|----------------------------+----------------+-----------------------------------------------|
| Source:                    | Destination:   | Command:                                      |
| conkeror-dir/              | ~/.conkerorrc/ | ln -s conkeror-dir/ ~/.conkerorrc             |
| emacs-dir/                 | ~/.emacs.d/    | ln -s emacs-dir/ ~/.emacs.d                   |
| stumpwm-dir/               | ~/.stumpwm.d/  | ln -s stumpwm-dir/ ~/.stumpwm.d               |
|----------------------------+----------------+-----------------------------------------------|
| stumpwm-dir/stumpwmrc.lisp | ~/.stumpwmrc   | ln -s stumpwm-dir/stumpwmrc.lisp ~/.stumpwmrc |
|----------------------------+----------------+-----------------------------------------------|

